(firstQuint)Integrated Diagnostic for Heart Failure.

 Patients with systolic heart failure (HF) implanted with Medtronic wireless implantable cardiac defibrillator (ICD) or cardiac resynchronization therapy device with defibrillation capabilities (CRT-D) devices will be enrolled in the study.

 The purpose of the study is to evaluate the usability of CareLink HFRS to manage a patient's heart failure.

